<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Former NRL WAG Phoebe Burgess has forged her own career path as an influencer.</p>

<p>And now the 31-year-old has landed a lucrative new deal, as a style ambassador for Specsavers Australia.</p>

<p>In an Instagram post on Friday, the mother-of-two was primped to perfection while modelling the latest in fake reading glasses.   </p>

<p>Specs-y lady! Phoebe Burgess, 31, modelled the latest in fake reading glasses in an Instagram post on Friday (pictured), as she lands a lucrative new gig with Specsavers Australia </p>

<p>Phoebe wore a white linen shirt dress with floral embroidery, accessorising with a pair of clear-rimmed non-prescription reading glasses. </p>

<p>Her blonde locks were styled semi-straight, and her makeup was glamorous. </p>

<p>'My non-glasses, glasses are the perfect pairing to simplify any of my louder outfit combos,' Phoebe told fans in the post's caption.  </p>

<p>Trying on a new look: 'My non-glasses, glasses are the perfect pairing to simplify any of my louder outfit combos,' Phoebe told fans. Pictured in a prior Instagram post </p>

<p>'The crystal clear trend brings a certain sophistication while the keyhole bridge throws it back for a vintage vibe.</p>

<p>'Who would have guessed that acetate plastic could be so chic?!' she continued.   </p>

<p>Phoebe often shares her updated wardrobe choices with her 80,000-plus Instagram following.</p>

<p>Fanbase: The mother-of-two often shares her updated wardrobe choices with her 80,000-plus Instagram following </p>

<p>Quieter lifestyle: Phoebe has been hunkering down at the picturesque surrounds amid the coronavirus pandemic, with daughter Poppy, three, and son Billy, one (both pictured) </p>

<p>Numerous photos see the former journalist stunning in tailored pants, double denim, cashmere sweaters, coats and statement sneakers, at her family's country estate in the New South Wales' Southern Highlands.</p>

<p>Phoebe has been hunkering down at the picturesque surrounds amid the coronavirus pandemic, with daughter Poppy, three, and son Billy, one.</p>

<p>The blonde beauty shares her children with ex-husband, Rabbitohs star Sam, 31, who she wed in 2015.</p>

<p>Ex-husband: The blonde beauty shares her children with ex-husband, Rabbitohs star Sam Burgess (pictured with their children), 31, who she wed in 2015 </p>
